(584,	'options_privacy_policy',	'<h2><strong>PRIVACY POLICY</strong></h2>\r\nThis Policy, read together with all other legal documents on the Website, shall be legally binding on any person or entity who accesses or uses the¬†<strong>[site_url]</strong>¬†Website (hereinafter referred to as the ‚ÄúWebsite‚Äù). The User shall be bound by all the Terms &amp; Conditions contained herein, as well as any regulations and laws applicable to the particular jurisdiction from which the User accesses the Website from.¬† Users are urged to read the Website‚Äôs Privacy Policy carefully. This Policy shall replace all previous versions.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>GENERAL</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>The owner(s) of the Website are committed to protecting and respecting the privacy of all of its User‚Äôs.</li>\r\n 	<li>The owner(s) of the Website will take all reasonable and legal steps to protect confidential information and will release information only to the relevant authorities under their request or in terms of any regulation which requires such and when necessary for a third-party integration.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>INFORMATION COLLECTED BY THE WEBSITE</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li><strong>Log Data:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>When a User visits the Website, the Website services may automatically log the standard data provided by the User‚Äôs web browser.</li>\r\n 	<li>This may include: The Users computer Internet Protocol (IP) address, browser type and version, the pages the User has visited, the time and date of these visits, the time spent on each page and other details.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Device Data:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>The Website may collect data about the device that the User is using to access the Website.</li>\r\n 	<li>This data collected may include: The device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, device settings and geo-location data.</li>\r\n 	<li>What we collect can depend on the individual settings