rt multiple roles per user</li>\n<li>bugfix: remove deprecated function calls for PHP 7.2 compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.1.1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: import multiple roles per user</li>\n<li>bugfix: remove deprecated function calls for PHP 7.2 compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.1.0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: added option to import password hash</li>\n<li>bug fix: changed filter priority for block user emails option</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.9</p>\n<ul>\n<li>bug fix: delete users that are no longer present in your file</li>\n<li>bug fix: disable delete missing users option for manual record matching</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.8</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improvement: compatibility with PHP 7.x</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.7</p>\n<ul>\n<li>added ACF to re-import options</li>\n<li>fixed import confirm screen</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.6</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed sending \'Welcome email\' for WordPress less than 4.3.1</li>\n<li>added re-import options to step 4</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.5</p>\n<ul>\n<li>added User ID to manual record matching</li>\n<li>added new option \'block email notification during import\'</li>\n<li>added ‚ÄòWelcome email‚Äô for new users that will be send to user when ‚ÄòBlock email notifications‚Äô option is disabled</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.4</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed changelog</li>\n<li>fixed excessive update requests</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.3</p>\n<ul>\n<li>improved security</li>\n<li>fixed import user roles</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.2</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed clear temp files</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>changed main plugin file name</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1.0.0</p>\n<ul>\n<li>User Import Add-On For WP All Import 4.0</li>\n</ul>\n<p>0.9.5</p>\n<ul>\n<li>added: auto update feature</li>\n</ul>\n<p>0.9.4</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed: re-run feature for users import</li>\n</ul>\n<p>0.9.3</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed: php notices</li>\n</ul>\n<p>0.9.2</p>\n<ul>\n<li>fixed: slowly admin interface issue</li>\n<li>fixed: admin notices</li>\n<li>fixed: php warnings</li>\n</ul>\n<p>0.9.1</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";}s:7: